Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.47,0:00:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.73,0:00:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不要大意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,女人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.87,0:00:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不是龙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,缇奥 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.02,0:00:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,缇奥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.78,0:00:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,香织啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我还好 就是有点累了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,缇奥 始他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,就你一个人吗 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.56,0:00:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静点 香织
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:01:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,火山喷发是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.02,0:02:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那始他们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.56,0:02:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 应该会跟在我后面回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,主人没有丝毫放弃的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是有什么计策
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,香织 主人叫我传话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,始吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 准确来说是说给你和缪的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他说「待会儿再见」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,香织
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.36,0:03:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊 那肯定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就算身处绝望险境
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,主人也一定能奇迹生还
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,相信他就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不去接爸爸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得相信始爸爸 完成好我们手上的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这之后再去接他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 不能把缪带去古卢恩大火山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.13,0:03:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那就先去爱尼森 让缪和妈妈见面怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.29,0:03:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 那就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那之后过了多少天了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,始 感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题 不过痊愈还需要点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.93,0:04:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 没事 毕竟希娅让我吸了血
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,月小姐 你为什么要坐上来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.49,0:04:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,极光的毒素基本都排出来了 应该没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我都说了没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 还是很让人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然这地方让人担心 不过能好好休息就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,也是 毕竟事情那么跌宕起伏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,也不知道是幸运还是倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人 马上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,暂时放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,始 看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是魔法阵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这是 空间操作魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是瞬间移动的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那种突然出现在背后的是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,祈愿人的未来 为自由之意志所掌控
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.38,0:06:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,奈兹·古卢恩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,太简单了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉就像无事一身轻了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,奈兹大人除了魔法好像没留下其他任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 攻略证明和魔法都到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来就看怎么逃出这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但是空间魔法很难掌控 没办法立刻使用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.69,0:06:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你有计策对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:07:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,外面应该已经完全被岩浆淹没了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,在岩浆里游着前进
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 别像看傻子一样看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我准备了潜水用的船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.62,0:07:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我想着之后梅尔基涅海底遗迹肯定用得上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.62,0:07:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,所以提前做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就看能不能挡得住岩浆了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微有点担心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,看来没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 船舵不听使唤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,要是火山喷发把我们喷出去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,径直往下…不对 好像在往斜下方走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那…就是说我们在往地底下钻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,月 希娅 看来短时间内是回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.89,0:08:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,只能先逃到能去的地方再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我会一直陪着你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,只要能陪着你我别无他求
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样 就算上刀山下火海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,只要能和你们在一起 我也愿意奉陪到底
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 弹药用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,月 吸我的血
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 我还…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,月
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,二位 你们是不是忘了个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,吸我的血吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.13,0:10:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,希娅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,吸了她很多血 暂时应该不会醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你醒了啊 感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢你若无其事泰然自若的关心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.00,0:10:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我的心情非常愉快 简直好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这里到底是哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道 虽然我很想调查一番
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但是宝物库给了缇奥 我也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,走一步算一步的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那不就是遇难了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是什么人 为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这骑乘工具是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,休想引开我们的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你们就是这样诱拐了那孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.82,0:11:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你们又来诱拐我们的小孩了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是说缪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴 区区一个兔人族少废话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚好像有东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.51,0:11:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,缪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:11:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,缪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不能再做这么危险的事了 能答应我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 答应你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好 那就行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉让你们担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,如你所见 生龙活虎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 所以你别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,香织一哭我就头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,再让我靠一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,缇奥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你 我一直相信着你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:13:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但是能像这样重逢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,给我点时间 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,来 主人 快奖励我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 那个小女孩是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 应该就是蕾蜜雅被拐走的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,确认公会支部长的委托完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.71,0:13:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,金级冒险者 南云阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,想必你们也有很多问题想问
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我想先让这孩子见见她母亲 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:13:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,海上被人目击的龙和船一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,作为王国士兵实在不能视而不见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们打算在爱尼森滞留一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,有空再详细解释可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,既然有机会详聊那就行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,等你们安顿好了再来拜访
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我说完了 不要继续围观了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我会以妨碍王国士兵公务为由逮捕你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 快回家 妈妈还等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我想见妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,也是 赶紧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,蕾蜜雅你冷静点 你的腿走不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊 蕾蜜雅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会把缪带回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:14:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 缪不是回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:15:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我得去接她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,缪 缪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是我没保护好你 对不起 缪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的 妈妈 缪就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,缪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈 你的腿怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,受伤了吗 很疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 快来救救妈妈 妈妈的腿很疼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,缪 你刚刚说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 果然你说的是爸爸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸？是叫我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你想屁吃 当然是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.00,0:15:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 妈妈她…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不用担心 缪 很快就能治好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.73,0:15:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说 别这么担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,蕾蜜雅再婚了？不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,蕾蜜雅也终于迎来了第二春 可喜可贺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此 这伤是被拐走缪的那些人害的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,香织 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 没问题 能治好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.31,0:16:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,为了不留后遗症
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,花点时间慢慢痊愈会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.11,0:16:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,痊愈之前会有些不便 不过一定能恢复的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,请放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我还听说这伤无人能医
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真不知道该如何感谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:17:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…说起来 你们和缪是如何相遇的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么缪会叫你爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,说来话长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,能再次见到女儿都是多亏了各位的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我会穷尽一生报答这份恩情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不用客气 您可是缪的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,听说你们要在这里滞留一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不如就住在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这样缪也会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不了 不用担心我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,栈桥附近正好有家好住宿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我还想把船修一修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 爸爸放下女儿不管可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 你要出门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你们总有一天还要再出发 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,正因为如此 分别之前就好好当她的爸爸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是说只能到分别的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,一直当她的爸爸也是可以的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟我也说了我会用一辈子报答这份恩情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这种玩笑就别开了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,没见气氛都变阴冷了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 真是受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.53,0:18:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 我的丈夫去世也快5年了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,缪也想要爸爸对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？爸爸就是爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 紧急集合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.84,0:18:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.49,0:18:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:19:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来 刚刚她说了先去向陛下报告吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,八重檻同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,关于清水的事情很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.93,0:19:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 很开心老师能幸存下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真得好好谢谢南云
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是他去救你们了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,而且还照顾着一个小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.00,0:19:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定他正慢慢找回曾经的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,或者说是在变化中慢慢成长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,太可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.27,0:19:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 听说他在危难之中救了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:19:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,具体情况是怎样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 既然都说差点丧命了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定还是很在意到底是怎么得救的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这…这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,您和南云之间发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会 还能有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我和他就是普通的师生关系而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.56,0:20:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 冷静点 你说话都变奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,南云 你对小爱做了什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.18,0:20:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 你向陛下报告的时候发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他们正式认定南云为异端分子了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 这样下定论未免太草率了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.02,0:20:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是不服从教会的强大力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但从结论来说南云的确拯救了乌尔镇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:21:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 不管怎么抗议他们就是不听
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.91,0:21:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,明明他们应该不能无视我的抗议才对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,将南云认定为异端分子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.11,0:21:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那不就等于否定了丰收女神的存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.82,0:21:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,很明显不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,现在回想起来 陛下他们的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.27,0:21:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好像也有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,的确让人在意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.73,0:21:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他们到底在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,南云已经很强了 他们还能派谁去找他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.47,0:21:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,八重檻同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.78,0:21:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,有些话南云只告诉了我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.62,0:21:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.91,0:21:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 关于教会祭拜的神 还有南云的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.96,0:21:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然毫无证据
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.71,0:21:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这件事非常重要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.49,0:22:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得必须尽早告诉大家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 海底的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:24.65,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Tears streaming down your sorrow face
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:30.65,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Came a long and painful road, you gave yourself away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:35.99,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You saw everything, heaven to hell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:42.41,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You say you need a self redemption, to mend the broken wings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:47.84,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Drowning in the dark, no place to be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.55,0:01:51.59,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}But I am by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:53.43,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You’re not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.68,0:01:59.35,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, shed a light so you won’t disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.56,0:02:05.31,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Cause I know where you belong, save your saddened heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:11.03,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}With a flashback, screaming out but still we’re holding on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:16.45,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Waiting for the break of dawn for a new day to begin
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.91,0:02:19.70,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, daylight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.29,0:02:25.04,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Stay a little while longer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:12.77,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全部　期待してみて幻だった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.77,0:22:17.27,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}信じたかった　縋りたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:23.99,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身体の底に開いた螺旋状の穴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:29.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}ボクだけじゃなく　キミにもなんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:38.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}許されることなど　もう望んじゃいない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.34,0:22:42.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱き寄せてもまた　わからないシルエット
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:47.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}躊躇いもなく傷つけた代償か
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:52.56,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}キミの側は　揺れてボクを離れた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:57.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:02.11,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:07.11,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}道を違える度に　ボクの後ろに穴が開く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:10.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伸びた一本の影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:16.62,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰もが手にし得る　小さな欠片で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:21.21,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何ができる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:26.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:31.22,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:12.77,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}期待的一切皆为虚空一场
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.77,0:22:17.27,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}破灭的希望　虚伪的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:23.99,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嵌入身体的伤口深不见底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:29.16,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不仅是我　你也背负同样的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:38.34,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早已不再奢望　求得谁人原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.34,0:22:42.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪怕怀中相拥　徒留轮廓难辨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:47.43,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}甘愿承伤不曾犹豫的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:52.56,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我步履蹒跚　忍痛离开你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:57.52,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明凛然在上　抛下两难抉择
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:02.11,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不断拷问你我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:07.11,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}几步对错　令我身负百孔千疮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:10.16,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}形单影只渐行渐远
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:16.62,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望碎片　谁人不曾拥有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:21.21,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又能作何挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:26.38,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明凛然在上　抛下两难抉择
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:31.22,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不断拷问你我
